high_descs: Walk across the room to the two sinks, facing the middle.
Pick up the pink soap from in between the two sinks.
Walk to face the sink on the right.
Rinse the soap in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Face the middle of the two sinks.
Put the pink soap down in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a bar of pink soap, putting it back in between the two sinks.

go to sink to the right

go to counter in between two sinks to the left

high_descs: Move to the sink on your left.
Pick up the soap on the sink.
Bring the soap to the right side sink.
Wash the soap in the right sink.
Bring the washed soap to the middle of the counter.
Put the soap on the counter.
